在1960年代，[[孟买|孟買]]的Mazagaon當地有一個小型的[[唐人街|中國城]] <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dhapa.com/indian-chinese-in-mumbai/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-11-30 |archive-date=2015-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101045625/http://www.dhapa.com/indian-chinese-in-mumbai/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 。[[中印边境战争|1962年中印边境战争]]之後，大多數中國人被視為叛徒而離開了該城鎮<ref name="khaleej">{{Cite news|title = Say sorry to the Indian Chinese|last = Abidi|first = S.N.M|date = 2008-02-28|work = [[Khaleej_Times|Khaleej Times]]|accessdate = 2008-10-08}}</ref> 。目前，孟買有400個家庭是來自中國的華裔<ref name="rediff">{{Cite web|url = http://www.rediff.com/news/2004/jan/23speca.htm|title = Happy Indian Chinese New Year|last = Someshwar|first = Savera R|date = 2007-01-23|work = [[Rediff.com|Rediff.com]]|accessdate = 2008-10-08|archive-date = 2021-04-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210426203850/https://www.rediff.com/news/2004/jan/23speca.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。關於中國寺廟和墓地均位於Mazagaon<ref name="rediff">{{Cite web|url = http://www.rediff.com/news/2004/jan/23speca.htm|title = Happy Indian Chinese New Year|last = Someshwar|first = Savera R|date = 2007-01-23|work = [[Rediff.com|Rediff.com]]|accessdate = 2008-10-08}}</ref>
